      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for CFD simulation must comply with a documented SQA plan including version control, regression testing, and release validation at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "SQA documentation is present and version control is enforced, but regression test suite coverage is incomplete for the hemolysis sub-model routines. Achieved level 3 does not meet the required level 4 for MRL 5."
