      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs used in validation must directly correspond to the hemolysis index quantities required for COU decision at Gradation 3.",
      "rationale": "Validation uses normalized hemolysis index (NIH) while COU requires absolute hemolysis index (MIH). Transformation between metrics introduces additional uncertainty not fully quantified. Achieved level 2."
