    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; all show achieved levels below required levels. Six factors remain not-assessed, representing epistemic gaps. Despite the credibility shortfalls, the package is accepted for submission pending supplemental validation data. Monte Carlo UQ results provide partial uncertainty coverage. Provenance chain traces from claim through validation results to experimental datasets.",
